metadata.name: The Library
metadata.description:
The Library,  
Mixed Media,  
5400px X 7200px,  
2022,

A gift to those who bid on ROOMs. 

This work is an exploration of the ready-made, found art, and hybridization of the ethereal introspective post internet aesthetic slowly developing within the space. Utilizing and mixing the known aesthetics of internet images, color gradients, screen tones, and noise with the graphics of MOCA

The text itself creates a nice critique aimed towards the space. A lot of rhetoric within the space is very reminiscent  of the first part of the paragraph. A lot of actions, however, are reminiscent of the last part.
